1. White House: Trump will decide within two weeks whether to take military action against Iran;
2. Semler Scientific announced a BTC increase plan: holding at least 10,000 by the end of 2025 and 105,000 by 2027;
3. People familiar with the matter: Revolut is actively exploring the issuance of its own stablecoin;
4. Aave DAO has repurchased more than 50,000 AAVE so far, with an average price of $199.74 and a floating profit of $3 million;
5. Jupiter DAO: will suspend voting until the end of 2025 to focus on products and community;
6. LayerZero has launched a second public hearing on whether to turn on the "fee switch";
7. Arizona Bitcoin Reserve Act HB 2324 passed in the Senate;
8. Abstract Chain's official X account is suspected to be stolen;
9. Trader AguilaTrades set up a TWAP order and is expected to increase the position by 2,000 BTC in 8 hours;
10. Airwallex CEO: It’s time to short Circle.
